<section class="mt-10 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
  <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Built-in primitives</h3>
    <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
      <li><strong>latency</strong> - fixed delay every request</li>
      <li><strong>latencyRange</strong> - random delay between min and max</li>
      <li><strong>fail</strong> - always return a fixed error status</li>
      <li><strong>failRandomly</strong> - fail at a given probability (0..1)</li>
      <li><strong>failNth</strong> - fail every Nth request, cyclically</li>
      <li><strong>failFirstN</strong> - fail the first N requests, then pass</li>
      <li><strong>rateLimit</strong> - cap requests per time window, return 429</li>
      <li><strong>throttle</strong> - limit response bandwidth in bytes/sec</li>
      <li><strong>mock</strong> - return a fixed response without hitting the network</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
  <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Highlights</h3>
    <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
      <li>Global + route-specific middleware chains</li>
      <li>Koa-style composable middleware model</li>
      <li>Custom middleware registry</li>
      <li>Optional global fetch replacement</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</section>

